page.title: 11Skipping Rhymes
page.content:
**************************************
Keep the kettle boiling never miss a loop, a loop etc.
**************************************
I'm a little bumpy car number forty eight I went round the corner,and then I pulled my brakes, my brakes did not work so I rolled down the hill, fell in the duckpond then stood still. The police came and took me to jail, how many bottles of ginger ale,1,2,3 etc.
**************************************
Under the moon over the stars, Under the moon over the stars, etc. **************************************
